customStats: Damage suffered by the bearer is increased by 15% whenever they have more than 50% HP, but damage suffered is reduced by 20% whenever they have less than 50% HP.
When the bearer suffers an AP, MP or Range removal, they gain 50 Power for 2 turns, stackable 10 times.

For each distance attack suffered, the bearer gains shield and loses ranged damage for 1 turn; stackable up to 5 times maximum. The damage penalty and shield values vary according to the distance between the bearer and their attacker.
The bearer gains 2 MP on odd turns and loses 1 MP on even turns.
At the start of each turn, the wearer pushes entities in close combat back 1 cell.

name.fr: Collier de la Dame du Hasard

customStats: If the bearer suffers a Lock or does not move during their turn, the bearer becomes Unlockable on their next turn for 1 turn.

At the end of each turn, the bearer attracts entities in a 3-cell cross around themself by 2 cells. If the bearer has no entities next to them at the end of their turn, they enter the Unmovable state until the start of their next turn. The state is removed if they suffer damage.

name.fr: Bottes de la Reine des Voleurs

customStats: The bearer gains 2 AP on even turns and loses 1 AP on odd turns.
When the bearer suffers damage in an element, they gain 3% resistance in that element for 2 turns, stackable 5 times.
At the end of their turn, the bearer removes 50 Dodge from adjacent enemies for 1 turn.

At the end of each turn, the bearer applies a start-of-turn poison for 1 turn in their best attack element on allied and enemy entities 2 cells away or less. The affected entities apply the poison again at the end of their turn on entities around them. The bearer also reduces poison damage received by 50%.
Increases one elemental characteristic per game turn: 300 to Chance, then 300 to Strength, then 300 to Agility, and then 300 to Intelligence.
